Users add to local system or ec2 :-

sudo adduser yadav                      :add user with password  
sudo adduser --disabled-password yadav  : add user without password

sudo usermod -aG sudo yadav             :to give sudo access to use....it will add user to sudo group...by default in starting user addeded to same group name
             OR
sudo nano /etc/sudoers                  : add->  yadav ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL
             OR
sudo visudo                             : it also open in same location /etc/sudoers

sudo groups yadav                       : to check user group
 
sudo deluser yadav                      : to delete user
